('MacBook Pro 13" (A1278, 2011) - Component Reference', 'Device Components/MacBook', '<p>Apple MacBook logic board 820-3115. Key rails: PPBUS_G3H, PP3V42_G3H, PPVRTC_G3H.</p><h2>Components (6)</h2><ul><li><strong>U7000</strong> - PMIC</li><li><strong>U2900</strong> - Charger IC - <code>ISL9239</code></li><li><strong>U6000</strong> - Retimer</li><li><strong>Q7005</strong> - MOSFET - PPBUS_G3H high-side</li><li><strong>Q7006</strong> - MOSFET - PPBUS_G3H low-side</li><li><strong>U5000</strong> - SMC</li></ul><h2>Test points &amp; known-good rails</h2><ul><li>PPBUS_G3H (PPBUS_G3H): 8.6-12.6 V @ off - Main system bus, present on battery/charger.</li><li>PP3V42_G3H (PP3V42_G3H): 3.42 V @ off - Always-on 3.42V rail.</li><li>PPVRTC_G3H (PPVRTC_G3H): 3.3 V @ off - RTC keep-alive.</li><li>PP3V3_S5 (PP3V3_S5): 3.3 V @ standby - 3.3V in S5.</li><li>PP5V_S5 (PP5V_S5): 5.0 V @ standby - 5V in S5.</li><li>PP1V8_S5 (PP1V8_S5): 1.8 V @ standby - 1.8V housekeeping.</li></ul>', 'Apple MacBook logic board 820-3115. Key rails: PPBUS_G3H, PP3V42_G3H, PPVRTC_G3H. U7000 PMIC   U2900 Charger IC ISL9239  U6000 Retimer   Q7005 MOSFET  PPBUS_G3H high-side Q7006 MOSFET  PPBUS_G3H low-side U5000 SMC   PPBUS_G3H PPBUS_G3H 8.6-12.6 V off PP3V42_G3H PP3V42_G3H 3.42 V off PPVRTC_G3H PPVRTC_G3H 3.3 V off PP3V3_S5 PP3V3_S5 3.3 V standby PP5V_S5 PP5V_S5 5.0 V standby PP1V8_S5 PP1V8_S5 1.8 V standby'),
