('Nintendo Switch (HAC-001) - Component Reference', 'Device Components/Nintendo', '<p>Nintendo Switch mainboard. Charging path: USB-C -> M92T36 -> BQ24193 -> battery. Dock video via P13USB.</p><h2>Components (5)</h2><ul><li><strong>U1</strong> - Charging IC - <code>M92T36</code> - USB-C PD / charging</li><li><strong>U2</strong> - Power IC - <code>M92T17</code> - Video/power routing</li><li><strong>U3</strong> - Display Mux - <code>P13USB</code> - USB/display mux</li><li><strong>U6</strong> - Battery Charger - <code>BQ24193</code> - Battery charger</li><li><strong>BQ</strong> - Regulator - <code>MAX77621</code> - Core regulator</li></ul><h2>Test points &amp; known-good rails</h2><ul><li>VBUS_5V (VBUS_5V): 5.0 V @ on - USB-C VBUS when charging.</li><li>SYS_VDD (SYS_VDD): 3.7-4.2 V @ on - Battery system rail.</li><li>3V3 (3V3): 3.3 V @ on - 3.3V rail.</li><li>1V8 (1V8): 1.8 V @ on - 1.8V rail.</li></ul>', 'Nintendo Switch mainboard. Charging path: USB-C -> M92T36 -> BQ24193 -> battery. Dock video via P13USB. U1 Charging IC M92T36 USB-C PD / charging U2 Power IC M92T17 Video/power routing U3 Display Mux P13USB USB/display mux U6 Battery Charger BQ24193 Battery charger BQ Regulator MAX77621 Core regulator VBUS_5V VBUS_5V 5.0 V on SYS_VDD SYS_VDD 3.7-4.2 V on 3V3 3V3 3.3 V on 1V8 1V8 1.8 V on'),
('PlayStation 4 Slim (CUH-2000) - Component Reference', 'Device Components/PlayStation', '<p>PS4 Slim mainboard. HDMI encoder MN864729. No-video usually HDMI IC or port. Standby 5V / 3.3V rails.</p><h2>Components (3)</h2><ul><li><strong>IC4001</strong> - HDMI IC - <code>MN864729</code> - HDMI encoder</li><li><strong>IC1001</strong> - PMIC - <code>BD7956</code> - APU power management</li><li><strong>CN1601</strong> - Connector - HDMI port</li></ul><h2>Test points &amp; known-good rails</h2><ul><li>STBY_5V (STBY_5V): 5.0 V @ standby - Standby supply present when plugged in.</li><li>3V3 (3V3): 3.3 V @ standby - Housekeeping 3.3V.</li></ul>', 'PS4 Slim mainboard. HDMI encoder MN864729. No-video usually HDMI IC or port. Standby 5V / 3.3V rails. IC4001 HDMI IC MN864729 HDMI encoder IC1001 PMIC BD7956 APU power management CN1601 Connector  HDMI port STBY_5V STBY_5V 5.0 V standby 3V3 3V3 3.3 V standby'),
('Apple iPhone 5 - Component Reference', 'Device Components/Apple', '<p>Apple iPhone 5 main logic board. Component set and rails are family-typical reference values; confirm exact values against the boardview/schematic for this unit.</p><h2>Components (10)</h2><ul><li><strong>J_DISP</strong> - Connector - Display FPC connector</li><li><strong>J_BATT</strong> - Connector - Battery FPC connector</li><li><strong>J_CHG</strong> - Connector - Charge port / dock connector</li><li><strong>J_FCAM</strong> - Connector - Front camera connector</li><li><strong>J_RCAM</strong> - Connector - Rear camera connector</li><li><strong>U_PMIC</strong> - PMIC - Main power management IC</li><li><strong>U_CHG</strong> - Charging IC - USB charging / interface IC</li><li><strong>U_AUDIO</strong> - Audio IC - Audio codec IC</li><li><strong>U_NAND</strong> - NAND Flash - Flash storage</li><li><strong>U2</strong> - USB Charging IC - <code>1610A1</code> - Tristar U2 USB / charging IC</li></ul><h2>Test points &amp; known-good rails</h2><ul><li>VBAT / PP_BATT_VCC (VBAT): 3.8 V @ off - Battery main rail (typically 3.0-4.35V with charge).</li><li>VBUS (VBUS_5V): 5.0 V @ on - USB VBUS when charging.</li><li>1V8 (PP1V8): 1.8 V @ on - 1.8V housekeeping rail (typical).</li><li>3V0 (PP3V0): 3.0 V @ on - 3.0V rail (typical).</li></ul>', 'Apple iPhone 5 main logic board. Component set and rails are family-typical reference values; confirm exact values against the boardview/schematic for this unit. J_DISP Connector  Display FPC connector J_BATT Connector  Battery FPC connector J_CHG Connector  Charge port / dock connector J_FCAM Connector  Front camera connector J_RCAM Connector  Rear camera connector U_PMIC PMIC  Main power management IC U_CHG Charging IC  USB charging / interface IC U_AUDIO Audio IC  Audio codec IC U_NAND NAND Flash  Flash storage U2 USB Charging IC 1610A1 Tristar U2 USB / charging IC VBAT / PP_BATT_VCC VBAT 3.8 V off VBUS VBUS_5V 5.0 V on 1V8 PP1V8 1.8 V on 3V0 PP3V0 3.0 V on'),
