('Amazon Fire 7 - Component Reference', 'Device Components/Amazon', '<p>Amazon Fire 7 main logic board. Component set and rails are family-typical reference values; confirm exact values against the boardview/schematic for this unit.</p><h2>Components (7)</h2><ul><li><strong>J_LCD</strong> - Connector - LCD FPC connector</li><li><strong>J_DIG</strong> - Connector - Digitizer FPC connector</li><li><strong>J_BATT</strong> - Connector - Battery FPC connector</li><li><strong>J_CHG</strong> - Connector - Charge port connector</li><li><strong>U_PMIC</strong> - PMIC - Main power management IC</li><li><strong>U_CHG</strong> - Charging IC - USB charging IC</li><li><strong>U_NAND</strong> - NAND Flash - Flash storage</li></ul><h2>Test points &amp; known-good rails</h2><ul><li>VBAT / PP_BATT_VCC (VBAT): 3.8 V @ off - Battery main rail (typically 3.0-4.35V with charge).</li><li>VBUS (VBUS_5V): 5.0 V @ on - USB VBUS when charging.</li><li>5V0 (PP5V0): 5.0 V @ on - 5V rail (typical).</li><li>1V8 (PP1V8): 1.8 V @ on - 1.8V housekeeping rail (typical).</li><li>3V3 (PP3V3): 3.3 V @ on - 3.3V rail (typical).</li></ul>', 'Amazon Fire 7 main logic board. Component set and rails are family-typical reference values; confirm exact values against the boardview/schematic for this unit. J_LCD Connector  LCD FPC connector J_DIG Connector  Digitizer FPC connector J_BATT Connector  Battery FPC connector J_CHG Connector  Charge port connector U_PMIC PMIC  Main power management IC U_CHG Charging IC  USB charging IC U_NAND NAND Flash  Flash storage VBAT / PP_BATT_VCC VBAT 3.8 V off VBUS VBUS_5V 5.0 V on 5V0 PP5V0 5.0 V on 1V8 PP1V8 1.8 V on 3V3 PP3V3 3.3 V on'),
